reviewText: Cute, cute, cute, we all love this movie (Casper can be a little annoying with how friendly he is, but nonetheless)  We are still watching this in February, great year round movie!
Title: Casper the Friendly Ghost and Friends: Trick or Treat

reviewText: Casper is the friendly ghost and especially uplifting on Halloween for families and adults in this negative world.  It is so well done and we loved it.  The vendor - I will use again; efficient, speedy and well done.  Thank you.
